story: Pwnky, a creature from the Black night of Inpinity Online, ventured through the digital realms with Dark bad eyes eyes that sparkled with curiosity, a Mechanic body body that shimmered with the essence of creativity, and a Laughing  mouth that resonated with the voices of countless creators. On this journey, Pwnky's Sad ear ears fluttered in the electronic winds, and Cool blue hair hair flowed like the rivers of code that shaped the landscape. Adorned with a Vikings hat hat crafted by the artisans of the net, Pwnky discovered the Horns, a relic that could unlock new realms in this infinite universe.
description: a new Pwnkey with Black night, Dark bad eyes, Mechanic body, Laughing , Sad ear, Cool blue hair, Vikings hat, Horns
